                                <condition>Macalister (1945, 53) notes that The monument has been intentionally broken up (probably for wall-building), <q>as is evident from a crow-bar mark on one of the fragments</q>. The monument has been intentionally broken up (probably for wall-building), as is evident from a crow-bar mark on one of the fragments. The lettering on the second fragment is badly injured by spalling. </condition>
